						Hogwarts Professor of the Magic Defense of Darkness.<br/>
						Subjects include defense against the magic of darkness, how to deal with dangerous magical creatures, and real magic martial arts.
						There is a jinx on which the professor in charge changes every year due to an accident or accident.
					</h4>
				</div><br/>

