						<img id="a" src="Aurora Sinistra.jpg"/>
						Aurora Sinistra.<br/>
						Professor of astronomy at Hogwarts.<br/>
						It is the only study that is nearly the same as the Muggle world. 
						However, studying stars is different from Muggle astronomy, and it is a technique demonstrated quite often by Dumbledore and other high-end magicians to understand what is happening. <br/>
						However, astrology is different from Divination that foretells the future. As you can see the current time, the movements of the stars indicate the current situation, but they cannot predict the future.
